    if (Either.isLeft(r)) errs.push(r.left);
    if (Either.isLeft(m)) errs.push(m.left);
    if (errs.length > 0) return yield* Effect.fail(errs);
    return c;
  });
```

`Effect.either` reifies each rule's failure; `Effect.all` runs every check without short-circuiting, and the collected `Left`s become a single `ReadonlyArray<FieldError>` in the error channel.

